      <p>You must be 18 or older to create an account. If you’re younger, grab a parent or guardian to help you use our services safely.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h3><i class="bi bi-globe-americas"></i> Using the Platform</h3>
      <p>Be respectful, honest, and lawful. No spam, no scams. Treat others like you’d want to be treated in their home.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h3><i class="bi bi-door-closed-fill"></i> Listings Are Your Responsibility</h3>
      <p>All listings and content should be accurate, fair, and not misleading. You're responsible for what you post, and for keeping it awesome.</p>
