      <p>All site content — code, design, and text — belongs to the developer unless otherwise noted. Please don’t copy without permission.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h3><i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise"></i> Changes to These Terms</h3>
      <p>These terms may change as we grow. We’ll notify you if anything big happens. Keep an eye on this page once in a while.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="terms-section">
      <h3><i class="bi bi-envelope-fill"></i> Contact Us</h3>
      <p>Need help or have a question? Reach out anytime at <strong>hchanda2003@gmail.com</strong>. We’re here for you.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</main>
